        Returns:

      • buildUpon

        public History.Builder buildUpon()
        Get a builder to modify a copy of this history. The builder returned will retain all internal information related to the states in the history, including any associated View state. It is safe to remove states from the builder and push them back on; nothing will be lost in those operations.
